videos.description: Armoni Brooks starts out hot for Houston, giving them an early lead over Oregon with triples on back-to-back possessions.
videos.headline: Brooks drains two 3-balls to start game

videos.description: Bol Bol drives baseline and tries to finish, but Brison Gresham stands his ground to pin the shot against the backboard.
videos.headline: Gresham glasses Bol's layup

videos.description: Brison Gresham takes the steal, and Galen Robinson Jr. throws it ahead to Armoni Brooks, who drains a 3-ball to extend the Cougars' lead.
videos.headline: Houston turns steal into triple

videos.description: Cedrick Alley Jr. tries to shoot over Bol Bol, but the 7' 2" big man rises up to swat it into the stands.
videos.headline: Bol shows off wingspan on big block

videos.description: Bol Bol stuffs Fabian White Jr., then Victor Bailey Jr. gets out in transition for the and-1 finish at the rim.
videos.headline: Bol's block leads to Bailey's and-1

videos.description: Will Richardson chucks a pass all the way down the court, finding Paul White for the wide-open layup to extend the Cougars' lead.
videos.headline: Richardson throws full-court pass for fast-break finish
